    README - Baptiste VILLAIN H2 G1 - Projet 2
    
*************************************************/


/***********
  FEATURES
************/

- Video player
- Play/Pause
- Drag&Drop Circular Volume button
- Drag&Drop Horizontal seekbar
- Toggle Mute
- Time display
- Toggle fullscreen
- Thumbnail
- Refresh the page but keep your informations with localStorage

- Playlist
- Generate playlist from JSON
- Next button / Prev button
- Toggle loop/next track

- Keyboard commands:
- left/right arrow: backward/forward currentTime
- up/down arrow: up/down volume
- m: toggle mute
- f: toggle fullscreen
- j/l: next/previous track

tips: hold shift to increase incrementation.

should do: 
- set volume on click.


/***********
   TECHNO
************/

- HTML/CSS
- JS
- JSON
- LocalStorage


/***********
   THANKS
************/

- DRIBBBLE
- STACKOVERFLOW
- MDN

bugs: if you have any troubles with drag&drop or thumbnail position, refresh the page without the inspector mode.
